{
    "strings": {
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_NAME": "Armorer",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_DESCRIPTION": "Armorer is a skilled fighter who makes use of a wide arsenal of weaponry to take down their foes.<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Metal Blaster is a good source of consistent ranged damage and Heavy Metal stacks.\n\n< ! > Frag Cannon is a powerful offensive skill, with its piercing and high damage.\n\n< ! > Scrap Thruster gives significant horizontal movement paired with a large area of effect.\n\n< ! > Alloyed Bulwark can be used to quickly save yourself, or as a buffer.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SUBTITLE": "Resourceful Tinkerer",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_LORE": "Transcribed recording recovered from a recon squad:\r\n\r\n#1 “Keep up, we’ve almost lost it, I’m pretty sure I damaged it a bit”\r\n\r\n#2 “I’m trying, I’m just...really tired”\r\n\r\n#3 “What even was that thing...it almost looked like one of those crazy birds...”\r\n\r\n#1 “What? No way. That thing was a walking hunk of metal, must’ve been some kind of malfunctioning machine”\r\n\r\n#3 “I’m telling you, there was a bird under all the machinery!”\r\n\r\n#1 “Yeah, sure, let’s just keep going”\r\n\r\nLoud thud is heard\r\n\r\n#3 “Crap, Calem just fell over...”\r\n\r\n#1 “Well get him back up, we have to move!”\r\n\r\n#3 “He’s not getting up; there’s some weird metal crusted over half his suit!”\r\n\r\nLoud metal scraping is heard in the distance, followed by a growing hum\r\n\r\n#1 “Shit”\r\n\r\nEnd of recording ",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..and so he left, searching for a new identity.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..and so he vanished, forever a blank slate.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Phoenix": "Phoenix",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Quetzalcoatl": "Quetzalcoatl",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_NAME": "Heavy Metal",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Armorer's attacks apply stacks of Heavy Metal to enemies, reducing their damage and movement speed. When taking damage, gain stacks of Bulk Up, increasing your armor and attack speed.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_NAME": "Metal Blaster",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agile.</style> Shoot a projectile for <style=cIsDamage>150% damage</style>, which explodes for <style=cIsDamage>75% damage</style>.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_NAME": "Frag Cannon",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_DESCRIPTION": "Fire a piercing laser for <style=cIsDamage>500% damage</style>. Consume stacks of Bulk Up to fire additional beams.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_NAME": "Scrap Thruster",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_DESCRIPTION": "Fly forward with unstable engines; shrapnel flies off around you for <style=cIsDamage>600% damage</style>.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_NAME": "Alloyed Bulwark",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_DESCRIPTION": "Release a burst of energy for <style=cIsDamage>300% damage</style>. If you are hit for significant damage shortly after releasing energy, gain max Bulk Up and heal all nearby allies.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_NAME": "Machine Curse",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION": "Send out a wave of nanobots, granting barrier and a damage boost to nearby allies. Detonate Heavy Metal on nearby enemies, dealing damage for each stack and applying Anti Healing to weakened targets.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Grand Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Repair Expert",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, use Alloyed Bulwark's damage absorption to heal at least 200% of your health."
    },
    "en": {
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_NAME": "Armorer",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_DESCRIPTION": "Armorer is a skilled fighter who makes use of a wide arsenal of weaponry to take down their foes.<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Metal Blaster is a good source of consistent ranged damage and Heavy Metal stacks.\n\n< ! > Frag Cannon is a powerful offensive skill, with its piercing and high damage.\n\n< ! > Scrap Thruster gives significant horizontal movement paired with a large area of effect.\n\n< ! > Alloyed Bulwark can be used to quickly save yourself, or as a buffer.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SUBTITLE": "Resourceful Tinkerer",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_LORE": "Transcribed recording recovered from a recon squad:\r\n\r\n#1 “Keep up, we’ve almost lost it, I’m pretty sure I damaged it a bit”\r\n\r\n#2 “I’m trying, I’m just...really tired”\r\n\r\n#3 “What even was that thing...it almost looked like one of those crazy birds...”\r\n\r\n#1 “What? No way. That thing was a walking hunk of metal, must’ve been some kind of malfunctioning machine”\r\n\r\n#3 “I’m telling you, there was a bird under all the machinery!”\r\n\r\n#1 “Yeah, sure, let’s just keep going”\r\n\r\nLoud thud is heard\r\n\r\n#3 “Crap, Calem just fell over...”\r\n\r\n#1 “Well get him back up, we have to move!”\r\n\r\n#3 “He’s not getting up; there’s some weird metal crusted over half his suit!”\r\n\r\nLoud metal scraping is heard in the distance, followed by a growing hum\r\n\r\n#1 “Shit”\r\n\r\nEnd of recording ",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..and so he left, searching for a new identity.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..and so he vanished, forever a blank slate.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Phoenix": "Phoenix",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Quetzalcoatl": "Quetzalcoatl",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_NAME": "Heavy Metal",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Armorer's attacks apply stacks of Heavy Metal to enemies, reducing their damage and movement speed. When taking damage, gain stacks of Bulk Up, increasing your armor and attack speed.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_NAME": "Metal Blaster",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agile.</style> Shoot a projectile for <style=cIsDamage>150% damage</style>, which explodes for <style=cIsDamage>75% damage</style>.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_NAME": "Frag Cannon",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_DESCRIPTION": "Fire a piercing laser for <style=cIsDamage>500% damage</style>. Consume stacks of Bulk Up to fire additional beams.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_NAME": "Scrap Thruster",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_DESCRIPTION": "Fly forward with unstable engines; shrapnel flies off around you for <style=cIsDamage>600% damage</style>.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_NAME": "Alloyed Bulwark",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_DESCRIPTION": "Release a burst of energy for <style=cIsDamage>300% damage</style>. If you are hit for significant damage shortly after releasing energy, gain max Bulk Up and heal all nearby allies.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_NAME": "Machine Curse",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION": "Send out a wave of nanobots, granting barrier and a damage boost to nearby allies. Detonate Heavy Metal on nearby enemies, dealing damage for each stack and applying Anti Healing to weakened targets.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Grand Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Repair Expert",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, use Alloyed Bulwark's damage absorption to heal at least 200% of your health."
    },
    "de": {
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_NAME": "Rüstungsschmied",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_DESCRIPTION": "Der Rüstungsschmied ist ein geübter Kämpfer, der ein breites Arsenal nutzt, um Feinde auszuschalten.<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Metallblaster verursacht zuverlässigen Fernkampfschaden und Stapel von Schwermetall.\n\n< ! > Splitterkanone ist eine starke offensive Fertigkeit mit Durchschlag und hohem Schaden.\n\n< ! > Schrottschub bietet starke horizontale Bewegung und große Flächenwirkung.\n\n< ! > Legierter Wall kann dich schnell retten oder als Schutzpuffer dienen.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SUBTITLE": "Einfallsreicher Tüftler",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_LORE": "Transkribierte Aufnahme eines Aufklärungstrupps:\r\n\r\n#1 „Weiter, wir haben es fast verloren. Ich bin ziemlich sicher, dass ich es etwas beschädigt habe.“\r\n\r\n#2 „Ich versuche es, ich bin nur... wirklich müde.“\r\n\r\n#3 „Was war dieses Ding überhaupt... es sah fast aus wie einer dieser verrückten Vögel...“\r\n\r\n#1 „Was? Niemals. Das Ding war ein wandelnder Metallklotz, bestimmt irgendeine defekte Maschine.“\r\n\r\n#3 „Ich sage dir, unter all der Maschinerie war ein Vogel!“\r\n\r\n#1 „Ja, klar, gehen wir einfach weiter.“\r\n\r\nEin lauter Schlag ist zu hören\r\n\r\n#3 „Mist, Calem ist gerade umgefallen...“\r\n\r\n#1 „Dann heb ihn auf, wir müssen weiter!“\r\n\r\n#3 „Er steht nicht auf; da ist eine seltsame Metallkruste über der Hälfte seines Anzugs!“\r\n\r\nIn der Ferne ist lautes Metallschaben zu hören, gefolgt von einem anschwellenden Summen\r\n\r\n#1 „Scheiße“\r\n\r\nEnde der Aufnahme ",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..und so ging er, auf der Suche nach einer neuen Identität.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..und so verschwand er, für immer ein unbeschriebenes Blatt.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Phoenix": "Phönix",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Quetzalcoatl": "Quetzalcoatl",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_NAME": "Schwermetall",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Die Angriffe des Rüstungsschmieds belegen Feinde mit Schwermetall, wodurch Schaden und Bewegungsgeschwindigkeit sinken. Bei erlittenem Schaden erhältst du Aufrüsten, was Rüstung und Angriffsgeschwindigkeit erhöht.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_NAME": "Metallblaster",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agil.</style> Feuere ein Projektil für <style=cIsDamage>150% Schaden</style>, das für <style=cIsDamage>75% Schaden</style> explodiert.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_NAME": "Splitterkanone",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_DESCRIPTION": "Feuere einen durchschlagenden Laser für <style=cIsDamage>500% Schaden</style>. Verbraucht Stapel von Aufrüsten, um zusätzliche Strahlen abzufeuern.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_NAME": "Schrottschub",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_DESCRIPTION": "Fliege mit instabilen Triebwerken nach vorne; Schrapnell fliegt um dich herum und verursacht <style=cIsDamage>600% Schaden</style>.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_NAME": "Legierter Wall",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_DESCRIPTION": "Entfessle einen Energiestoß für <style=cIsDamage>300% Schaden</style>. Wenn du kurz danach erheblichen Schaden erleidest, erhältst du maximales Aufrüsten und heilst alle nahen Verbündeten.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_NAME": "Maschinenfluch",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION": "Sende eine Welle Nanobots aus, die nahen Verbündeten Barriere und erhöhten Schaden gewährt. Lässt Schwermetall auf nahen Feinden detonieren, verursacht Schaden pro Stapel und blockiert Heilung bei geschwächten Zielen.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Grand Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Repair Expert",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, use Alloyed Bulwark's damage absorption to heal at least 200% of your health."
    },
    "es-419": {
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_NAME": "Armero",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_DESCRIPTION": "El Armero es un combatiente hábil que usa un amplio arsenal para derribar a sus enemigos.<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Desintegrador de metal inflige daño a distancia constante y acumula Metal pesado.\n\n< ! > Cañón de fragmentos es una habilidad ofensiva poderosa, perforante y de mucho daño.\n\n< ! > Propulsor de chatarra ofrece gran movimiento horizontal con amplia área de efecto.\n\n< ! > Baluarte aleado puede salvarte rápidamente o servir como protección.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SUBTITLE": "Manitas ingenioso",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_LORE": "Grabación transcrita recuperada de un escuadrón de reconocimiento:\r\n\r\n#1 “Sigan, casi lo perdemos. Estoy casi seguro de que lo dañé un poco.”\r\n\r\n#2 “Lo intento, solo estoy... muy cansado.”\r\n\r\n#3 “¿Qué era esa cosa...? Casi parecía uno de esos pájaros raros...”\r\n\r\n#1 “¿Qué? Imposible. Eso era un pedazo de metal andante, debió ser alguna máquina defectuosa.”\r\n\r\n#3 “Te digo que había un pájaro debajo de toda esa maquinaria.”\r\n\r\n#1 “Sí, claro, sigamos avanzando.”\r\n\r\nSe oye un fuerte golpe\r\n\r\n#3 “Mierda, Calem acaba de caerse...”\r\n\r\n#1 “Pues levántalo, tenemos que movernos.”\r\n\r\n#3 “No se levanta; hay una costra metálica extraña cubriendo la mitad de su traje.”\r\n\r\nSe oye un fuerte raspado metálico a la distancia, seguido de un zumbido creciente\r\n\r\n#1 “Mierda”\r\n\r\nFin de la grabación ",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..y así se fue, buscando una nueva identidad.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..y así desapareció, para siempre una página en blanco.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Phoenix": "Fénix",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Quetzalcoatl": "Quetzalcóatl",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_NAME": "Metal pesado",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Los ataques del Armero aplican Metal pesado a los enemigos, reduciendo su daño y velocidad de movimiento. Al recibir daño, obtiene Reforzarse, aumentando su armadura y velocidad de ataque.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_NAME": "Desintegrador de metal",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_PRIMARY_BLASTER_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Ágil.</style> Dispara un proyectil que inflige <style=cIsDamage>150% de daño</style> y explota causando <style=cIsDamage>75% de daño</style>.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_NAME": "Cañón de fragmentos",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SECONDARY_GUN_DESCRIPTION": "Dispara un láser perforante que inflige <style=cIsDamage>500% de daño</style>. Consume acumulaciones de Reforzarse para disparar rayos adicionales.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_NAME": "Propulsor de chatarra",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_UTILITY_ROLL_DESCRIPTION": "Vuela hacia adelante con motores inestables; la metralla sale despedida a tu alrededor e inflige <style=cIsDamage>600% de daño</style>.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_NAME": "Baluarte aleado",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_BOMB_DESCRIPTION": "Libera una explosión de energía que inflige <style=cIsDamage>300% de daño</style>. Si recibes daño significativo poco después, obtienes Reforzarse al máximo y curas a todos los aliados cercanos.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_NAME": "Maldición mecánica",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SPECIAL_VIRUS_DESCRIPTION": "Envía una ola de nanobots que otorga barrera y aumento de daño a aliados cercanos. Detona Metal pesado en enemigos cercanos, causando daño por acumulación y aplicando Anticuración a objetivos debilitados.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_MASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Monsoon.",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Grand Mastery",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Repair Expert",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, use Alloyed Bulwark's damage absorption to heal at least 200% of your health."
    },
    "es-ES": {
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_NAME": "Armero",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_DESCRIPTION": "El Armero es un combatiente hábil que usa un amplio arsenal para derribar a sus enemigos.<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Desintegrador de metal inflige daño a distancia constante y acumula Metal pesado.\n\n< ! > Cañón de fragmentos es una habilidad ofensiva poderosa, perforante y de mucho daño.\n\n< ! > Propulsor de chatarra ofrece gran movimiento horizontal con amplia área de efecto.\n\n< ! > Baluarte aleado puede salvarte rápidamente o servir como protección.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_SUBTITLE": "Manitas ingenioso",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_LORE": "Grabación transcrita recuperada de un escuadrón de reconocimiento:\r\n\r\n#1 “Sigan, casi lo perdemos. Estoy casi seguro de que lo dañé un poco.”\r\n\r\n#2 “Lo intento, solo estoy... muy cansado.”\r\n\r\n#3 “¿Qué era esa cosa...? Casi parecía uno de esos pájaros raros...”\r\n\r\n#1 “¿Qué? Imposible. Eso era un pedazo de metal andante, debió ser alguna máquina defectuosa.”\r\n\r\n#3 “Te digo que había un pájaro debajo de toda esa maquinaria.”\r\n\r\n#1 “Sí, claro, sigamos avanzando.”\r\n\r\nSe oye un fuerte golpe\r\n\r\n#3 “Mierda, Calem acaba de caerse...”\r\n\r\n#1 “Pues levántalo, tenemos que movernos.”\r\n\r\n#3 “No se levanta; hay una costra metálica extraña cubriendo la mitad de su traje.”\r\n\r\nSe oye un fuerte raspado metálico a la distancia, seguido de un zumbido creciente\r\n\r\n#1 “Mierda”\r\n\r\nFin de la grabación ",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..y así se fue, buscando una nueva identidad.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..y así desapareció, para siempre una página en blanco.",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Phoenix": "Fénix",
        "Tatertotticus_Armorer_Quetzalcoatl": "Quetzalcóatl",
