        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_GRANDMASTERYACHIEVEMENT_DESCRIPTION": "As Armorer, beat the game or obliterate on Typhoon",
        "ACHIEVEMENT_TATERTOTTICUS_ARMORER_HEALINGACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Armorer: Repair Expert",
